<item>
            <title>[HBASE-7157] Report Metrics into an HBase table</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7157</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Right now metrics are sent using ServerLoad and RegionLoad to the master.  We should store those(and other) metrics in a table.  Storing these metrics in a table will allow the LoadBalancer to have more context.  In addition those metrics will be useful for the ui.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
